class that inherits all the methods and properties from another class

single inheritance
only one parent and one child are there

multiple inheritance
2 parents to only one child inheritance

multi-level inheritance
parent to child to child1 inheritance

hierarchical inheritance
only one parent and 2 child's

Hybrid inheritance
eg:-
Here father class act as parent1
mother class act act as child class to father class
but child class act as a child to both father and mother class(mother class act as parent2 to child but not father class)


